postcran <- goldman %>% select(Inst,Sex,lhml,lheb,lhhd) %>% filter(Sex %in% c(0,1), Inst %in% c('KU','MNdAE','NHM', 'SfAP')) %>% na.omit()

##  Welch Two Sample t-test
